<p>This is a collaboration between <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561382331" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1267048); return false;">Ihp</a></span> and myself for collab con featuring the Chicago Spirit and Factory. By the way, this is a GoI Format double feature, so there's a good chance you missed half of the story.</p>
<p>Chicago Spirit Format: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-1">http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-1</a><br />
Factory Format: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-2">http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragment:chicago-factory-2</a></p>
