<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561382331" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561382331" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;">Rounderhouse</a></span> for their invaluable crit.</p>

